oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Little Jimmy Dickens and Rex Allen at Sam's Silver Spur (17034)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Dickens, Little Jimmy, 1920-2015; Allen, Rex, 1920-1999; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing Little Jimmy Dickens on November 14 and Rex Allen on December 6 at the Sam's Silver Spur. Poster features metal photoplates of Jimmy Dickens and Rex Allen Jr. Purchase order 17034. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/21190.
